{"__ud_title":"Deep research skill","__ud_tags":["aiskills"],"__ud_update_time":1770806981135,"__ud_create_time":1770796156721,"__ud_draft":false,"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":1,"id":"desk"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Deep research skill"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"https://github.com/wshuyi/deep-research","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer nofollow","class":null}}],"text":"https://github.com/wshuyi/deep-research"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Deep Research Methodology (8-step) - Transform vague topics into high-quality research reports with systematic fact extraction and verifiable conclusions"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":1,"id":"Deep-Research"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Deep Research"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"https://github.com/wshuyi/deep-research/blob/main/README_CN.md","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer nofollow","class":null}}],"text":"中文文档"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A Claude Code Skill that transforms vague topics into high-quality, deliverable research reports using a systematic 8-step methodology."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"The-Problem"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"The Problem"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"When researching complex topics, you often face:"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Information overload"},{"type":"text","text":": Too many sources, hard to distinguish quality"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Fuzzy conclusions"},{"type":"text","text":": \"I feel like X\" instead of evidence-based reasoning"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Missing traceability"},{"type":"text","text":": Can't verify where conclusions came from"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Time-sensitivity blindness"},{"type":"text","text":": Using outdated information in fast-moving fields like AI"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Traditional research is time-consuming, and conclusions are often unreliable."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"The-Solution"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"The Solution"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Deep Research provides a "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"systematic 8-step methodology"},{"type":"text","text":" that:"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Tiered source evaluation"},{"type":"text","text":": L1 (official docs) > L2 (blogs) > L3 (media) > L4 (community)"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Fact cards with citations"},{"type":"text","text":": Every claim traceable to its source"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Time-sensitivity assessment"},{"type":"text","text":": Automatic handling of fast-changing fields"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Verifiable conclusions"},{"type":"text","text":": \"Fact → Comparison → Conclusion\" explicit chains"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Deliverable output"},{"type":"text","text":": Boss-readable reports with one-line summaries"}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"Requirements"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Requirements"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Claude Code CLI"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Web search tools (WebSearch, Tavily MCP, or Exa MCP)"}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"Installation"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Installation"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"Option-1-Git-Clone-Simplest"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Option 1: Git Clone (Simplest)"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"git clone https://github.com/wshuyi/deep-research.git\ncp -r deep-research/skills/deep-research ~/.claude/skills/"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"Option-2-Plugin-Marketplace"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Option 2: Plugin Marketplace"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"/plugin marketplace add wshuyi/deep-research\n/plugin install deep-research@wshuyi/deep-research"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"Option-3-Third-party-Marketplaces"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Option 3: Third-party Marketplaces"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"After the repo gets 2+ stars, it will be automatically indexed by "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"https://skillsmp.com","target":"_blank","rel":"nofollow","class":null}}],"text":"SkillsMP"},{"type":"text","text":". Search for \"deep-research\" there."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"Usage"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Usage"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Natural language triggers:"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"深度调研 [topic]\" / \"Deep research on [topic]\""}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"帮我调研 [topic]\" / \"Research [topic] for me\""}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"对比分析 X 和 Y\" / \"Compare X and Y\""}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"写调研报告\" / \"Write a research report\""}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"Workflow-8-Steps"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Workflow (8 Steps)"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Step 0: Problem type identification\nStep 0.5: Time-sensitivity assessment (BLOCKING for AI/tech topics)\nStep 1: Problem decomposition & boundary definition\nStep 2: Source tiering & authority locking\nStep 3: Fact extraction & evidence cards\nStep 4: Build comparison framework\nStep 5: Reference alignment\nStep 6: Fact → Conclusion derivation chain\nStep 7: Use case validation (sanity check)\nStep 8: Deliverable formatting\n"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"Output-Structure"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Output Structure"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"~/Downloads/research/<topic>/\n├── 00_问题拆解.md          # Problem decomposition\n├── 01_资料来源.md          # Source documentation\n├── 02_事实卡片.md          # Fact cards\n├── 03_对比框架.md          # Comparison framework\n├── 04_推导过程.md          # Derivation process\n├── 05_验证记录.md          # Validation records\n└── FINAL_调研报告.md       # Final deliverable\n"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"Example"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Example"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"User: 深度调研 REST API 和 GraphQL 的区别\n\nClaude: [Executes 8-step methodology]\n- Identifies as: Concept Comparison type\n- Creates fact cards from official specs\n- Uses 8-dimension comparison framework\n- Validates with real-world scenarios\n- Outputs structured report with citations\n"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"Key-Features"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Key Features"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Feature Description "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Source Tiering"},{"type":"text","text":" L1-L4 hierarchy ensures conclusion traceability "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Time-sensitivity"},{"type":"text","text":" Auto-detects fast-moving fields (AI, crypto, etc.) "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Fact Cards"},{"type":"text","text":" Every claim has source, confidence level, applicability "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Explicit Derivation"},{"type":"text","text":" No \"I feel like\" - only mechanism-based conclusions "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Deliverable Output"},{"type":"text","text":" One-line summary + structured chapters + citations"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"FAQ"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"FAQ"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Q: How is this different from just asking Claude to research something?"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A: This skill enforces a systematic methodology with intermediate artifacts, source verification, and explicit reasoning chains. Results are traceable and verifiable."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Q: Does it work for non-technical topics?"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A: Yes, the methodology applies to any research topic. The 5 problem types (concept comparison, decision support, trend analysis, problem diagnosis, knowledge organization) cover most use cases."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Q: How does it handle outdated information?"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A: Step 0.5 assesses time-sensitivity. For high-sensitivity fields (AI, blockchain), it enforces 6-month time windows and requires version number citations."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":1,"id":"Deep-Research深度调研"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Deep Research（深度调研）"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"https://bgithub.xyz/wshuyi/deep-research/blob/main/README.md","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer nofollow","class":null}}],"text":"English"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"一个 Claude Code 技能，通过系统化的 8 步方法论，将模糊主题转化为高质量、可交付的调研报告。"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"痛点"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"痛点"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"在调研复杂主题时，你经常面临："}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"信息过载"},{"type":"text","text":"：来源太多，难以区分质量"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"结论模糊"},{"type":"text","text":"：「我感觉像 X」而非基于证据的推理"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"无法追溯"},{"type":"text","text":"：不知道结论从何而来"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"时效盲区"},{"type":"text","text":"：在 AI 等快速变化领域使用过时信息"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"传统调研耗时长，结论往往不可靠。"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"解决方案"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"解决方案"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Deep Research 提供"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"系统化的 8 步方法论"},{"type":"text","text":"："}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"资料分层评估"},{"type":"text","text":"：L1（官方文档）> L2（博客）> L3（媒体）> L4（社区）"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"带出处的事实卡片"},{"type":"text","text":"：每条论断都可追溯到来源"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"时效敏感性评估"},{"type":"text","text":"：自动处理快速变化的领域"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"可验证的结论"},{"type":"text","text":"：「事实 → 对照 → 结论」显式推导链"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"可交付的输出"},{"type":"text","text":"：老板能读、能转述、能追溯的报告"}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"环境要求"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"环境要求"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Claude Code CLI"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"网络搜索工具（WebSearch、Tavily MCP 或 Exa MCP）"}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"安装方式"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"安装方式"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"方式-1Git-Clone最简单"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"方式 1：Git Clone（最简单）"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"git clone https://github.com/wshuyi/deep-research.git\ncp -r deep-research/skills/deep-research ~/.claude/skills/"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"方式-2插件市场"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"方式 2：插件市场"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"/plugin marketplace add wshuyi/deep-research\n/plugin install deep-research@wshuyi/deep-research"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"方式-3第三方市场"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"方式 3：第三方市场"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"仓库获得 2+ stars 后会被 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"https://skillsmp.com","target":"_blank","rel":"nofollow","class":null}}],"text":"SkillsMP"},{"type":"text","text":" 自动收录，可直接搜索「deep-research」安装。"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"使用方法"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"使用方法"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"自然语言触发："}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"「深度调研 [主题]」"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"「帮我调研 [主题]」"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"「对比分析 X 和 Y」"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"「写调研报告」"}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"工作流程8-步法"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"工作流程（8 步法）"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Step 0: 问题类型判断\nStep 0.5: 时效敏感性评估（AI/技术类主题必须执行）\nStep 1: 问题拆解与边界界定\nStep 2: 资料分层与权威锁定\nStep 3: 事实抽取与证据卡片\nStep 4: 建立对比/分析框架\nStep 5: 参照物基准对齐\nStep 6: 从事实到结论的推导链\nStep 7: 用例验证（Sanity Check）\nStep 8: 可交付化处理\n"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"输出结构"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"输出结构"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"~/Downloads/research/<topic>/\n├── 00_问题拆解.md          # 问题类型、子问题列表\n├── 01_资料来源.md          # 所有资料链接和摘要\n├── 02_事实卡片.md          # 抽取的事实及出处\n├── 03_对比框架.md          # 选定的框架和填充\n├── 04_推导过程.md          # 事实→结论的推导\n├── 05_验证记录.md          # 用例验证和回查\n└── FINAL_调研报告.md       # 最终交付报告\n"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"示例"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"示例"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"用户：深度调研 REST API 和 GraphQL 的区别\n\nClaude：[执行 8 步方法论]\n- 判断类型：概念对比型\n- 从官方规范创建事实卡片\n- 使用 8 维度对比框架\n- 用实际场景验证\n- 输出带引用的结构化报告\n"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"核心特性"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"核心特性"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"特性 说明 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"资料分层"},{"type":"text","text":" L1-L4 层级确保结论可追溯 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"时效敏感"},{"type":"text","text":" 自动检测快速变化领域（AI、加密货币等） "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"事实卡片"},{"type":"text","text":" 每条事实都有来源、置信度、适用范围 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"显式推导"},{"type":"text","text":" 不说「我感觉像」，只有机制对比得出的结论 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"可交付输出"},{"type":"text","text":" 一句话总结 + 结构化章节 + 引用来源"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"常见问题"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"常见问题"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Q: 这和直接让 Claude 调研有什么区别？"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A: 本技能强制执行系统化方法论，有中间产物、来源验证、显式推理链。结果可追溯、可验证。"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Q: 非技术类主题也能用吗？"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A: 可以，方法论适用于任何调研主题。5 种问题类型（概念对比、决策支持、趋势分析、问题诊断、知识梳理）覆盖大多数场景。"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Q: 如何处理过时信息？"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A: Step 0.5 评估时效敏感性。对于高敏感领域（AI、区块链），强制执行 6 个月时间窗口，要求标注版本号。"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"许可证"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"许可证"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"MIT License - 详见 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"https://bgithub.xyz/wshuyi/deep-research/blob/main/LICENSE","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer nofollow","class":null}}],"text":"LICENSE"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"作者"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"作者"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"wshuyi"},{"type":"text","text":" - "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"https://bgithub.xyz/wshuyi","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer nofollow","class":null}}],"text":"GitHub"}]}]}]}]}